pan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">π͡ρ</span>(ό)</span>  <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"ιδ\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ιδ\">ιδ</span>´ <span data-text=\"καλανδῶν\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"Kalendae\">κ(αλανδῶν)</span>  <span data-text=\"μαρτίου\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"Martius\">(<em>scil.</em> μαρτίου)</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.2)</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἰησοῦς Χριστός\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἰησοῦς\"><span data-text=\"Ἰησοῦς\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"Ἰησοῦς\"><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ἰ</span>(ησοῦς)</span></span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Χριστός\"><span data-text=\"Χριστός\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"Χριστός\">Χ(ριστός)</span></span></span>  <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.3)</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"ἐτελεὺτησεν\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"τελευτάω\">ἐτελεὺτησεν</span>  <span data-text=\"ὡ\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">ὡ</span>  <span data-text=\"μακαριώτατος\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"μακάριος\">μακαριώτατος</span>  <span data-text=\"Ἀνατῶλης\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Ἀνατόλις\">Ἀνατῶλης</span>  <span data-text=\"πρεσβύτερος\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"πρεσβύτερος\">πρεσβύτερος</span>  <span data-text=\"μηνὶ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">μηνὶ</span>  <span data-text=\"φεβρουαρίου\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"Februarius\">φεβρουαρίου</span>  <span data-text=\"πρό\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"πρό\">πρό</span>  <span data-text=\"ιδ\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ιδ\">ιδ</span>  <span data-text=\"καλανδῶν\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"Kalendae\">καλανδῶν</span>  <span data-text=\"μαρτίου\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"Martius\">μαρτίου</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.2)</span>  <span data-text=\"Ἰησοῦς\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"Ἰησοῦς\">Ἰησοῦς</span>  <span data-text=\"Χριστός\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"Χριστός\">Χριστός</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.3)</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>†<span data-text=\"ἐτελεὺτησεν\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"τελευτάω\">Ε<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Τ</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Λ</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ΕΝ</span></span><span data-text=\"ὡ\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">Ω</span><span data-text=\"μακαριώτατος\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"μακάριος\">ΜΑΚΑΡΙΩ<span class=\"error\" title=\"hi tag with rend=stacked is not supported!\">Τ</span></span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀνατῶλης\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀνατῶλης\"><span data-text=\"Ἀνατῶλης\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Ἀνατόλις\">Α<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ν͡Α͡Τ͡Ω</span>Λ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Η͡Σ</span></span></span></span><span data-text=\"πρεσβύτερος\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"πρεσβύτερος\">Π<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ρ</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Β</span>Σ</span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"μηνὶ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"μείς\"><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Μ</span></span><span data-text=\"φεβρουαρίου\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"Februarius\">ΦΕΒΡ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ο͡Υ</span>ΑΡΙ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ο͡Υ</span></span><span data-text=\"πρό\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"πρό\"><span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Π͡Ρ</span></span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"ιδ\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ιδ\">ΙΔ</span><span data-text=\"καλανδῶν\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"Kalendae\">Κ</span><span data-text=\"μαρτίου\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"Martius\">(<em>scil.</em> ΜΑΡΤΙΟΥ)</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἰησοῦς Χριστός\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἰησοῦς\"><span data-text=\"Ἰησοῦς\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"Ἰησοῦς\"><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ι</span></span></span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Χριστός\"><span data-text=\"Χριστός\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"Χριστός\">Χ</span></span></span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"ἐτελεὺτησεν\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"τελευτάω\">ΕΤΕΛΕΥΤΗΣΕΝ</span><span data-text=\"ὡ\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">Ω</span><span data-text=\"μακαριώτατος\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"μακάριος\">ΜΑΚΑΡΙΩΤΑΤΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"Ἀνατῶλης\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Ἀνατόλις\">ΑΝΑΤΩΛΗΣ</span><span data-text=\"πρεσβύτερος\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"πρεσβύτερος\">ΠΡΕΣΒΥΤΕΡΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"μηνὶ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">ΜΗΝΙ</span><span data-text=\"φεβρουαρίου\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"Februarius\">ΦΕΒΡΟΥΑΡΙΟΥ</span><span data-text=\"πρό\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"πρό\">